                <head>No. 104.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Beach</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-05-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 5, 1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>We hold Santos’s citizenship fully established and not debatable, and expect
                    treatment accordingly. Wachusett will soon return Guayaquil bearing full
                    instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>BAYARD.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
